Finding {{current_finding.id}} ({{current_finding.severity}}):

- Location: {{current_finding.location}}
- Finding: {{current_finding.text}}
- Fix recommendation: {{current_finding.fix_recommendation}}

Resolution options:
- Apply recommended fix (Recommended): apply as proposed
- Custom fix: I'll describe a different fix
- Waive: leave as-is; accept the degradation (only valid
